# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# RTX 4090 + Arch Linux Optimized Configuration
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# REQUIRED
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
MONGO_PASSWORD=CHANGE_THIS_SECURE_PASSWORD

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# GPU OPTIMIZATION (RTX 4090 - 24GB VRAM)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
CUDA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=0
NVIDIA_VISIBLE_DEVICES=all
NVIDIA_DRIVER_CAPABILITIES=compute,utility

# Ollama GPU settings (optimized for 4090)
OLLAMA_NUM_GPU=1
OLLAMA_GPU_LAYERS=99999
OLLAMA_NUM_PARALLEL=8              # 4090 can handle 8 parallel requests
OLLAMA_MAX_LOADED_MODELS=4         # Keep 4 models in VRAM
OLLAMA_MAX_QUEUE=128               # Large queue for fast GPU
OLLAMA_FLASH_ATTENTION=1           # Enable flash attention (faster)
OLLAMA_KV_CACHE_TYPE=f16           # Use FP16 for KV cache (more VRAM efficient)

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PERFORMANCE (32GB RAM + Fast Network + NVMe)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
MAX_CONCURRENT_REQUESTS=50         # Your network can handle it
CAMOUFOX_MAX_INSTANCES=10          # Run 10 browsers in parallel
VISION_BATCH_SIZE=8                # Process 8 images at once
EXTRACTION_BATCH_SIZE=16           # Process 16 documents at once

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AI MODELS (Use larger/better models with GPU)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
VISION_MODEL=qwen3-vl              # Better vision model
OCR_MODEL=qwen3-vl                 # Better OCR
EXTRACTION_MODEL=qwen2.5:32b       # Larger model (GPU can handle it)
EMBEDDING_MODEL=bge-m3             # Keep same
REASONING_MODEL=deepseek-r1:14b    # Add reasoning model

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ARCH LINUX SPECIFIC
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
DATA_PATH=/data
TZ=America/New_York

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NETWORK OPTIMIZATION
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
DISCOVERY_TIMEOUT=5                # Fast network, lower timeout
DISCOVERY_RETRY=2                  # Fewer retries needed
HTTP_KEEPALIVE=true                # Reuse connections
TCP_NODELAY=1                      # Disable Nagle's algorithm

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# STORAGE (NVMe Optimization)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
MONGODB_WIRED_TIGER_CACHE_SIZE=4   # 4GB cache for MongoDB
MONGODB_SYNC_DELAY=5               # Faster sync on NVMe

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OPTIONAL
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# HF_TOKEN=your_token
